'''Saul Almeida''' (born June 4, 1989) is an American [[mixed martial artist]] currently competing in the [[Lightweight (MMA)|Lightweight]] division.

==Mixed martial arts career==
===Early career===
Almeida made his professional debut in October 2008, defeating Iann de Oliveira via unanimous decision. He would then win his next 6 bouts, earning them mostly by decision before losing to Pete Jeffrey via guillotine choke submission at CES MMA: First Blood on September 17, 2010. Almeida then won his next 2 bouts, defeating Bobby Reardanz and Cody Stevens both by unanimous decision before making his Bellator debut.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/fighters/saul-almeida-the-spider|title=Saul Almeida|publisher=Tapology.com}}</ref>

===Bellator MMA===
Almeida made his Bellator debut on August 20, 2011 at [[Bellator 48]]. He faced Tateki Matsuda and won via unanimous decision.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bellator.com/articles/Bellator-48-Live-Results-Saul-Almeida-146-lbs.-vs.-Tateki-Matsuda-145.25-lbs.|title=Bellator 48 Live Results: Saul Almeida (146 lbs.) vs. Tateki Matsuda (145.25 lbs.)|publisher=Bellator.com}}</ref>

Almeida next faced [[Matt Bessette]] at [[Bellator 63]] on March 30, 2012. He lost the fight via unanimous decision.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/bouts/52347-bellator-63-matt-the-mangler-bessette-vs-saul-the-spider-almeida|title=Matt Bessette vs. Saul Almeida|publisher=Tapology.com}}</ref>

Almeida was expected to face UFC veteran [[Kurt Pellegrino]] at [[Bellator 108]] on November 15, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://prommanow.com/2013/07/22/kurt-pellegrino-to-come-out-of-retirement-to-face-saul-almeida-at-bellator-mma-in-november/|title=Kurt Pellegrino To Come Out Of Retirement To Face Saul Almeida At Bellator MMA In November|publisher=ProMMANow.com|date=July 22, 2013}}</ref> However, Pellegrino pulled out of the fight due to injury.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mmajunkie.com/2013/10/injury-forces-kurt-pellegrino-from-bellator-108-new-opponent-sought-for-almeida|title=Injury forces Kurt Pellegrino from Bellator 108, new opponent sought for Almeida|publisher=MMAJunkie.com|date=October 18, 2013}}</ref>

Almeida faced [[Goiti Yamauchi]] at [[Bellator 109]] on November 22, 2013. He lost the fight via knockout in the first round.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sherdog.com/news/news/Bellator-109-Results-PlaybyPlay-Updates-59741#goiti-yamauchi--saul-almeida|title=Saul Almeida vs. Goiti Yamauchi|publisher=Sherdog.com|date=November 22, 2013}}</ref>

Almeida faced Andrew Fisher in a [[Bellator_MMA:_Season_Ten#Featherweight_tournament_bracket|Bellator Season 10 Featherweight Tournament]] alternate bout on February 28, 2014 at [[Bellator 110]]. He won the fight via unanimous decision.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sherdog.com/news/news/Bellator-110-Results-PlaybyPlay-Updates-64235#andrew-fisher-saul-almeida|title=Saul Almeida vs. Andrew Fisher|publisher=Sherdog.com|date=February 28, 2014}}</ref>

